title: The Sleepover Club - Season 2 Episode 9 - Blast From the Past
description:
Based on the popular books by Rose Impey, this comedy drama series features five 12-year-old girls on their quest for identity, individuality, belonging, family, friendship and how to have the most fun while trying to deny the existence of boys. 

We will be following with Season 2 (the current season) as individual episodes in a few days. Episodes will be posted out of order, so please no PMs or comments about missing episodes.
